  "keyFeatures": [
    "JWT authentication with HTTP-only refresh token cookies",
    "Backtracking algorithm for conflict-free schedule generation",
    "Priority-based rule scoring system (Strategy Pattern)",
    "11 built-in optimization rules (NO_GAPS, PREFER_MORNING, COMPACT_DAYS, etc.)",
    "Returns top 3 optimized schedule combinations",
    "Full CRUD for subjects, professors, sections, and rules",
    "Saved schedules management",
    "Swagger/OpenAPI interactive documentation",
    "PostgreSQL with Prisma ORM"
  ],
